on Zambians to vote for MMD in the local government elections to
be held on December 30.
</P>
<P>
Chiluba appealed to his countrymen to give his government a
little more time to improve their welfare as the rampant poverty
in the country could not be solved overnight.
</P>
<P>
After his release last June Kaunda said he will retire from
party politics.
</P>
<P>
Kaunda was arrested on December 25 of 1997 for alleged
involvement in the coup attempt on October 28 of the same year.
