<HEADLINE> Sichuan Encourages Foreign Participation in Reorganization </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHENGDU, December 28 (Xinhua) -- The government of southwest
China's Sichuan Province has adopted a policy encouraging
foreign businesses to participate in mergers, acquisitions and the
reorganization of local enterprises.
</P>
<P>
