<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, December 27 (Xinhua) -- Catherine Raney won the
3,000-meter race and Derek Parra triumphed in the 5,000-meter
Sunday on the first day of the U.S. Allround Speedskating
Championships in Wisconsin.
</P>
